# üçΩÔ∏è Hungry Vibes

A quick recipe finder web app for Taylor, a busy professional who wants to decide what to cook using ingredients already in the kitchen.

## Features
- Search recipes by main ingredient
- Responsive foodie-themed interface
- Recipe cards with images, recipe name, and links to full details
- Error handling and user tips
- Powered by TheMealDB API

## How to Use
1. Type a single ingredient (e.g., chicken, potato, rice, macaroni).
2. Press Enter or "Search".
3. Click on recipe cards to view details.

## Demo
- [Live Demo](https://codesandbox.io/p/sandbox/hungry-vibes-4h7t7t)
- [CodeSandbox Source](https://codesandbox.io/s/your-hungry-vibes)

## Tech Stack
- React.js (Frontend)
- Vanilla CSS for styling
- [TheMealDB](https://www.themealdb.com/api.php) for recipe data

---

## User Persona
**Taylor**, a busy professional, wants help cooking at home based on what's in the kitchen.

---

## AI Work Process
This app was designed, discussed, and incrementally improved using AI-led guidance for design, component structure, styling, error handling, final branding, and submission preparation.
